criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria: • Be between 60 and 74 years old;

          -  Have a diagnosis of breast cancer, with staging I or II;

          -  Being in treatment for breast cancer (hormone therapy);

        Exclusion Criteria: • Absolute contraindication for performing physical exercises

          -  Severe depression assessed by the Geriatric Depression Scale

          -  Malnutrition (degrees I, II and III), detected by the Body Mass Index (BMI), according
             to WHO criteria.
